To localize the addon for a certain language:

  - Install language pack of the wanted language
    (https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/$VERSION/$PLATFORM/xpi/$LANG.xpi)
  - Pass '--pref intl.locale.requested=$LANGUAGE_CODE' to web-ext run
  - Add translations to _locales/$LANGUAGE_CODE/messages.json and l10n/*.ini files
